{
  "message": "fix: smooth banner close button hover animation (#3736)\n\nRemove oversized min-h-11/min-w-11 touch targets from banner dismiss\nbuttons that caused a jarring hover highlight over a 44px area around a\n14px icon. Use consistent p-1.5 padding with rounded-md and explicit\ntransition-colors duration-150 for a smooth, proportional hover effect.\nAlso add transition-colors duration-150 to UpdateProgressBanner dismiss\nbutton which had no transition at all.\n\nCloses #3734\n\nSigned-off-by: Andy Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
